<hr class="clear-both" />
<h4>Authorised representative</h4>
<p class="mb-10">
  This is the person authorised to enter into contracts with the NSW government on behalf of your business. These contact details will not appear on your profile and are not available to buyers.
</p>

{{dds/checkbox-input
  isSimple=true
  field=(mut form.same_as_above)
  label="Same as above"
  class="minor"
  onChange=(action "sameClicked")
}}

<div class="row">
  {{dds/text-input
    isSimple=true
    label-text="First name"
    class="col-lg-18"
